          </p>
          <a class="btn btn-primary services-inquire">Inquire</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-3 m-2" style="width: 40rem;">
        <img
          class="card-img-top"
          src="/images/school-dance-card.jpg"
          alt="Card image cap"
        />
        <div class="card-body">
          <h4 class="card-title">School/Corporate Events</h4>
          <p>Price: $399</p>
          <p class="card-text">Up to 3 hours of music for a school or corporate
            event. Additional time may be added for $100/hr. Two large PAs
            included, enough to fill a room with hundreds of people. Lighting
            options available.</p>
          <a class="btn btn-primary services-inquire">Inquire</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
<!-- Inquiry Modal -->
<div id="inquiryModal" class="modal">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered" role="document">
    <!-- Modal content -->
    <div class="modal-content" style="width:400px;">
      <span class="close2">&times;</span>
      <h3 class="text-center">Inquiry</h3>
      <form id="inquiryForm">
        {{! NAME }}
        <div class="mb-2">
          <label for="inputName" class="form-label">Name</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="inputName" required />
        </div>
        {{! EMAIL }}
        <div class="mb-2">
          <label for="inputEmail" class="form-label">Email Address</label>
          <input
            type="email"
            class="form-control"
            id="inputEmail"
            aria-describedby="emailHelp"
            required
          />
          <div id="emailHelp" class="form-text">We'll never share your email
            with anyone else.
          </div>
        </div>
        {{! PHONE }}
        <div class="mb-2">
          <label for="inputPhone" class="form-label">Phone</label>
          <input
            type="tel"
            class="form-control"
            id="inputPhone"
            aria-describedby="phoneHelp"
          />
          <div id="emailHelp" class="form-text">(Optional)</div>
        </div>
        {{! PACKAGE }}
        <div class="mb-2">
          <label for="inputPackage" class="form-label">Are you interested in a
            specific package?</label>

          <select
            id="inputPackage"
            class="form-select"
            aria-label="Default select example"
          >
            <option selected>No</option>
            <option value="Wedding Ceremony">Wedding Ceremony</option>
            <option value="Wedding Reception">Wedding Reception</option>
            <option value="Wedding Bundle">Wedding Bundle</option>
            <option value="School/Corporate Event">School/Corporate Event</option>
            <option value="Private Event">I need a DJ for a private Event</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        {{! MESSAGE BODY }}
        <div class="mb-2">
          <label for="inputMessage" class="form-label">Message</label>
          <textarea
            id="inputMessage"
            name="inquiry"
            cols="40"
            rows="5"
            class="form-control"
            required
          ></textarea>
        </div>
        {{! PREFERRED CONTACT METHOD }}
        <div>
          <label class="form-label">How would you like us to contact you?</label>
          {{! Email Option }}
          <div class="form-check">
            <input
              class="form-check-input"
              type="radio"
              name="flexRadio"
              id="emailSelect"
              checked
            />
            <label class="form-check-label" for="flexRadioDefault1">
              Email
            </label>
          </div>
          {{! Phone Option }}
          <div class="form-check">
            <input
              class="form-check-input"
              type="radio"
              name="flexRadio"
              id="phoneSelect"
            />
            <label class="form-check-label" for="flexRadioDefault2">
              Phone
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
      </form>
      <p id="submitMessage" style="display:none;">Inquiry Successfully
        Submitted. We'll get back to you within 48 hours.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<script src="/js/services.js"></script>